  "name": "Building Blocks - ADA Geochemistry Building Blocks repository",
  "abstract": "Building blocks for Astromat Data Archive (ADA) geochemistry metadata profiles,\nusing the OGC Building Blocks pattern.\n",
  "description": "Modular schema components for ADA analytical technique metadata. Imports shared\nschema.org and CDIF property building blocks from the CDIF Building Blocks repository.\n",
